Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\3c&H26AF7A&\an8\blur3\fnMS Mincho\fs42\4c&H26AF7A&\1c&H08571F&\2c&HFFFFFF&}{\kf36}大{\kf55}切{\kf29}を{\kf7}見{\kf23}つ{\kf35}け{\kf21}た{\kf70}魂{\kf74}も
